| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5726 — Recovery Inhibition (shinyhunters)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f3e537e-ec18-533b-97c3-2cf1018622ec"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
